{"_path":"/maps/_fe-framework/fe-framework","_dir":"_fe-framework","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"前端框架","description":"前端开发各阶段的工具集合，包括 UI 框架、元框架、组件方案、动画库等。","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"前端框架"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"前端框架"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"前端框架是在前端开发不同阶段，用以简化开发的工具集合。它们提供了一种组织代码的方式，使得开发者可以专注于业务逻辑，而不是底层的技术细节。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"子领域导航"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"子领域导航"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"ui-框架"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"UI 框架"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_fe-framework/ui-frameworks/vue"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Vue"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_fe-framework/ui-frameworks/react"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"React"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_fe-framework/ui-frameworks/angular"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Angular"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_fe-framework/ui-frameworks/vue-reactive"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Vue 响应式"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"元框架"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"元框架"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_fe-framework/meta-frameworks/nuxt"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Nuxt"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_fe-framework/meta-frameworks/nuxt-security"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Nuxt Security"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"组件方案"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"组件方案"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_fe-framework/component-solutions/web-components"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Web Components"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_fe-framework/component-solutions/micro-frontend"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"微前端"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"动画与交互"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"动画与交互"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_fe-framework/motion/blockies-animation"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Blockies Animation"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_fe-framework/motion/lottie"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Lottie"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"类型系统"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"类型系统"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_fe-framework/type-system/utility-types"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Utility Types"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_fe-framework/type-system/zod"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Zod"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"资源管理"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"资源管理"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_fe-framework/assets/iconify"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Iconify"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"知识点"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"知识点"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"sharing-state-with-islands-architecture"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Sharing State with Islands Architecture"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"MAXI FERREIRA 阐述的在岛模式组件中管理状态的思路也可以用于低代码场景。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"We have several options for choosing a store. Astro recommends the nanostores library in their documentation, which is what we'll use for our example, but several UI frameworks already come with a built-in solution—Svelte has Stores, Preact has Signals (as does Solid), and Vue has the Reactivity API."}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"第一次见到有人在公开场合说 Vue 的 Reactive API 是可以用于管理状态的。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/20231010125234.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"新的状态管理办法结合了事件通知和统一的状态管理库。一种替代的版本是使用回调函数。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"模板语言为何终将变成糟糕的编程语言"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"模板语言为何终将变成糟糕的编程语言？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"许多框架坚持使用模板语言而非将 HTML/CSS 融入 JavaScript。但模板语言的演化轨迹证明：\n它们 inevitably 会添加条件、循环、作用域、宏等特性，最终变成一门表达能力远逊于真正编程语言的\"内部平台\"。\n模板语言假设存在一个\"不怕代码但不够聪明写真正代码\"的用户群体，但实践中这个群体并不存在——\n设计师根本不想写代码，而开发者需要原生表达能力。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"动态语言的优势在于运行时可重新配置行为，这对构建赋予用户自由度的复杂应用至关重要。\n大多数 React 替代方案针对的是\"网站\"而非\"应用\"场景，它们铺设的是走惯的小径，\n却从未超越这些路径。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://acko.net/blog/get-in-zoomer-we-re-saving-react/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Get in Zoomer, We're Saving React"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"编译型框架的崛起是否推翻了模板语言批评"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"编译型框架的崛起是否推翻了模板语言批评？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2022 年的批评认为 React 替代方案\"只适合网站\"。但 2025-2026 年的数据显示：\nSvelte 开发者满意度达 92%，SolidJS 达 90%，均超越 React 的 78%。\nSolidJS 已进入 NASA JPL 等高性能场景，SvelteKit 支撑起复杂全栈应用。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"编译时优化与细粒度响应式的组合证明：模板/编译方案可以在保持开发体验的同时，\n达到甚至超越虚拟 DOM 方案的灵活性。Vue 3.6 的 Vapor 模式（绕过虚拟 DOM）\n进一步模糊了\"模板 vs JSX\"的界限。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"修正结论"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：模板语言 vs JSX 之争未分胜负，取决于场景——\n内容型网站倾向模板（Astro、Svelte），高度交互应用倾向 JSX（React、Solid）。\n2022 年对编译型框架的悲观预测已被证伪。"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"子领域导航","depth":2,"text":"子领域导航","children":[{"id":"ui-框架","depth":3,"text":"UI 框架"},{"id":"元框架","depth":3,"text":"元框架"},{"id":"组件方案","depth":3,"text":"组件方案"},{"id":"动画与交互","depth":3,"text":"动画与交互"},{"id":"类型系统","depth":3,"text":"类型系统"},{"id":"资源管理","depth":3,"text":"资源管理"}]},{"id":"知识点","depth":2,"text":"知识点"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_fe-framework:fe-framework.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_fe-framework/fe-framework.md","_stem":"6.maps/_fe-framework/fe-framework","_extension":"md"}